ActNational Capital Act
SubjectNational Capital Commission-Wesley Clover Foundation ** Leasing **
PrecisOrder approving the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to enter into a LEASE with the WESLEY CLOVER FOUNDATION for a term of twenty-one years commencing on January 1, 2014, with two renewal options of fourteen years each, to occupy a property located at 401 and 411 Corkstown Road, in Ottawa.
